Class DaylightRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Record
      • domain.DaylightRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DaylightRecord
extends Record
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class extends the Record class. This class also implements the serializable interface. It has few functions to calculate the difference between the sunset/sunrise time for the particular date of the invoking object.
